Meet Isabella ( Bella )🐾💛 Our New Family Member

When we visited the pet shop with my husband , We was just looking for a friend for Terry — someone to keep him company at home. But I had no idea that a puppy would end up choosing me.

Bella… she reached out, hugged me like she was saying, “Take me home, I’m yours.”
It felt like magic — not just a decision, but a moment of fate.

Now we’re home, and we’re learning to become a little family.
Terry’s still adjusting — he’s older and calm, while she’s a little firecracker, full of energy, bouncing around everywhere.
I’m introducing them slowly, gently… it’s a journey. But I truly believe they’ll become best friends in time. ❤️

For now, I’m just doing my best to give them both the love and patience they need to build that bond. 🐶🐶
Fyi : Terry -7 years old boy (chowchow), Bella-3 month old girl (golden retriever) 👩🏼‍❤️‍💋‍👨🏼
